   Juergens, Andreas; Witt, Taina, Univ KwaZulu Natal, Sch Biol \& Conservat Sci, ZA-3209 Pietermaritzburg, South Africa.
   Gottsberger, Gerhard, Univ Ulm, Bot Garden, D-89081 Ulm, Germany.
   Gottsberger, Gerhard, Univ Ulm, Herbarium, D-89081 Ulm, Germany.},
