   Ahrne, Karin, Swedish Univ Agr Sci, Swedish Species Informat Ctr, SE-75007 Uppsala, Sweden.
   Ockinger, Erik, Swedish Univ Agr Sci, Dept Ecol, SE-75007 Uppsala, Sweden.},
